WEBVTT

00:00:13.105 --> 00:00:14.345
Grandma!

00:00:14.425 --> 00:00:15.585
What if something happens to her?

00:00:15.665 --> 00:00:16.865
Your grandma is going to be okay.

00:00:18.225 --> 00:00:19.385
Can you forgive me?

00:00:21.505 --> 00:00:22.745
But there is something…

00:00:22.825 --> 00:00:24.585
I need you to help me with.

00:00:25.185 --> 00:00:27.145
You’ve become much cuter than before.

00:00:27.985 --> 00:00:28.985
Come and give Daddy a hug.

00:00:37.625 --> 00:00:39.345
Come with me, okay?

00:01:51.465 --> 00:01:53.865
Hey. Hey.

00:01:55.185 --> 00:01:56.305
Boyfriend.

00:01:57.865 --> 00:01:58.945
Oh…

00:01:59.025 --> 00:02:00.265
Look who's here.

00:02:00.345 --> 00:02:02.065
How did you know I was here?

00:02:02.905 --> 00:02:04.345
DinDin told me.

00:02:05.025 --> 00:02:07.065
Come on, let's go home.

00:02:07.145 --> 00:02:08.985
-Can you walk?
-Sure!

00:02:11.465 --> 00:02:12.305
Careful now.

00:02:17.305 --> 00:02:18.665
Nava? What’s wrong?

00:02:20.345 --> 00:02:21.345
Nava. Nava.

00:02:22.305 --> 00:02:23.425
My stomach hurts.

00:02:23.505 --> 00:02:24.745
It hurts.

00:02:35.305 --> 00:02:39.105
SEVERAL MONTHS EARLIER

00:02:50.865 --> 00:02:52.145
Hey there.

00:02:53.665 --> 00:02:55.385
-How’s it going?
-On track.

00:02:55.905 --> 00:02:56.825
Let me see.

00:03:02.265 --> 00:03:03.505
This is amazing.

00:03:04.225 --> 00:03:05.145
Gorgeous.

00:03:05.225 --> 00:03:07.785
You know that the client loves your work?

00:03:08.945 --> 00:03:10.665
You're gonna make us rich.

00:03:11.465 --> 00:03:13.185
-Yes, Ma’am.
-Keep it up.

00:03:13.265 --> 00:03:14.545
Go for it.

00:03:25.665 --> 00:03:28.785
The 15-second board is roughly like this.

00:03:28.865 --> 00:03:34.265
And the KV really fits
the "Future of Pattaya" theme.

00:03:35.985 --> 00:03:39.585
This isn't what I had in mind at all.

00:03:39.665 --> 00:03:42.505
And isn't this KV too cluttered?

00:03:42.585 --> 00:03:44.425
-But--
-Can you clean it up a bit?

00:03:44.505 --> 00:03:46.545
But these are what you chose…

00:03:46.625 --> 00:03:49.705
It doesn't look good now. Just fix it.

00:03:53.385 --> 00:03:54.545
Yes, Ma'am.

00:03:54.625 --> 00:03:57.065
Go. Hurry up and fix it.

00:03:57.145 --> 00:04:01.265
Don't worry, he'll be done in 30 minutes.

00:04:01.345 --> 00:04:03.905
Let's move on to the wardrobe.

00:04:03.985 --> 00:04:06.025
Relax, have some water first.

00:04:06.105 --> 00:04:06.985
Okay?

00:04:09.345 --> 00:04:12.025
Chai, put some more light in the back.

00:04:18.105 --> 00:04:21.545
Mr. Nava! Why isn't the model on set yet?!

00:04:22.064 --> 00:04:23.465
I'll check right now.

00:04:24.865 --> 00:04:26.105
Where is she?

00:04:26.625 --> 00:04:27.825
She won't come out.

00:04:27.905 --> 00:04:31.345
-Why won’t she come out?
-Says it's too hot. I tried my best.

00:04:33.305 --> 00:04:34.545
There are 30 minutes left.

00:04:34.625 --> 00:04:35.745
Can you shoot something else for now?

00:04:35.825 --> 00:04:37.225
How can I? There’s nothing to--

00:04:37.305 --> 00:04:38.945
-Nava!
-Yes, Ma’am!

00:04:39.025 --> 00:04:41.465
What are you doing?!
The client is waiting!

00:04:41.545 --> 00:04:43.985
-Go and get her now.
-Alright, fine.

00:04:44.505 --> 00:04:46.265
It's boiling out here!

00:04:46.905 --> 00:04:48.825
Why did you want to shoot in the sun?

00:04:51.785 --> 00:04:53.345
Okay, you can pose now.

00:04:54.065 --> 00:04:57.185
Great. Please change a pose.

00:04:57.265 --> 00:04:58.625
Looks good.

00:04:58.705 --> 00:05:00.225
Stop! Stop right there!

00:05:00.305 --> 00:05:02.065
-Yes.
-That's the wrong product!

00:05:02.745 --> 00:05:03.945
C… Cut.

00:05:04.025 --> 00:05:06.465
-Not this one?
-No!

00:05:06.985 --> 00:05:08.585
One moment, please.

00:05:08.665 --> 00:05:11.185
-Please hold this one.
-When will it be over?

00:05:11.265 --> 00:05:12.985
-Just a moment, please.
-It's so hot.

00:05:13.065 --> 00:05:14.105
Nava!

00:05:14.185 --> 00:05:17.465
-Yes, Ma’am?
-We're running out of time! And it’s hot!

00:05:17.545 --> 00:05:18.745
Yes! Please bear with me for a moment.

00:05:18.825 --> 00:05:20.425
We only have the slot until noon!

00:05:20.505 --> 00:05:22.945
Please have a look at the monitor.

00:05:37.505 --> 00:05:38.345
Wake up!

00:05:38.425 --> 00:05:39.665
Yes, Ma’am?

00:05:40.265 --> 00:05:43.265
The deadline is 9 a.m!
How can you finish it if you’re sleeping?!

00:05:43.785 --> 00:05:45.385
Yes, I’ll be as quick as possible.

00:05:45.465 --> 00:05:47.225
Are you sure?

00:05:47.305 --> 00:05:50.345
If you miss this, the company
is finished because of you.

00:05:50.425 --> 00:05:51.545
I… I'll get it done.

00:05:51.625 --> 00:05:53.025
Then hurry up!

00:05:53.105 --> 00:05:56.225
The deadline’s coming and you're sleeping!

00:06:31.505 --> 00:06:32.705
Do I…

00:06:33.225 --> 00:06:34.425
have cancer, Doctor?

00:06:35.745 --> 00:06:38.785
Yes. You are in stage two.

00:06:39.705 --> 00:06:43.105
Fortunately, it’s still treatable.

00:06:44.505 --> 00:06:46.585
If we start the treatment soon,

00:06:47.265 --> 00:06:49.145
there’s a high chance of recovery.

00:06:51.425 --> 00:06:54.665
Please make an appointment
when you’re ready.

00:06:56.105 --> 00:06:56.985
Nava.

00:06:57.825 --> 00:07:00.225
You're too sick to work.
Just go get treated.

00:07:00.305 --> 00:07:01.625
You can’t work for me.

00:07:01.705 --> 00:07:03.105
I can handle it.

00:07:03.185 --> 00:07:04.865
Handle what? Look at your condition.

00:07:04.945 --> 00:07:06.625
I really can.

00:07:07.145 --> 00:07:10.785
You can’t. Besides, I’ve already
found someone to replace you.

00:07:10.865 --> 00:07:12.065
I can really do this, please.

00:07:12.145 --> 00:07:15.625
Just go. I'll pay your severance.

00:07:15.705 --> 00:07:17.545
Now, everyone, back to work.

00:07:42.825 --> 00:07:44.305
THANWARIN HOSPTIAL

00:07:44.385 --> 00:07:46.025
Are you a relative of Mr. Nava?

00:07:46.105 --> 00:07:48.105
Yes, I’m his boyfriend.

00:07:48.185 --> 00:07:49.945
What’s happening to Nava?

00:07:53.425 --> 00:07:55.625
Mr. Nava has stage two cancer.

00:07:57.825 --> 00:08:00.705
Stage two… cancer?

00:08:01.305 --> 00:08:07.825
Yes, we've tried
to contact him for treatment,

00:08:08.785 --> 00:08:10.345
but he never showed up.

00:08:11.625 --> 00:08:13.985
The patient’s condition
has weakened so much.

00:08:14.665 --> 00:08:16.985
We must start treatment immediately

00:08:17.665 --> 00:08:20.545
before it progresses further.

00:08:32.385 --> 00:08:33.385
Nava.

00:08:35.545 --> 00:08:37.105
How are you?

00:08:38.945 --> 00:08:41.264
Please discuss this with him.

00:08:42.425 --> 00:08:43.465
Yes.

00:08:43.545 --> 00:08:44.545
Thank you so much.

00:08:44.625 --> 00:08:45.505
Please excuse me.

00:08:52.305 --> 00:08:53.585
Nava,

00:08:56.225 --> 00:08:58.945
why did you keep this from me?

00:09:00.785 --> 00:09:02.665
Why didn't you tell me?

00:09:07.745 --> 00:09:09.305
Because I knew.

00:09:11.145 --> 00:09:14.345
I knew you'd be devastated.

00:09:25.425 --> 00:09:26.785
Let's break up.

00:09:29.745 --> 00:09:31.105
Nava…

00:09:34.465 --> 00:09:36.265
I'm going to die anyway.

00:09:38.345 --> 00:09:39.945
Leaving now…

00:09:40.705 --> 00:09:42.865
or when I'm gone, it’s all the same.

00:09:46.465 --> 00:09:47.545
No,

00:09:50.345 --> 00:09:52.185
I'm not breaking up with you.

00:09:52.985 --> 00:09:54.665
I'm not going anywhere.

00:09:55.745 --> 00:09:57.425
You’re going to be okay.

00:09:58.465 --> 00:10:01.745
The doctor said it's not terminal yet.

00:10:01.825 --> 00:10:03.185
If we start now, there's still a chance--

00:10:03.265 --> 00:10:04.665
What's the point, Sky?!

00:10:06.225 --> 00:10:07.745
It's cancer.

00:10:08.505 --> 00:10:10.185
I'm going to die anyway.

00:10:10.265 --> 00:10:11.865
Treatment is just more torture.

00:10:13.745 --> 00:10:15.265
Don’t think like that.

00:10:15.785 --> 00:10:20.785
The doctor confirmed that there's
still a good chance you’ll recover.

00:10:23.185 --> 00:10:24.145
Enough.

00:10:26.905 --> 00:10:28.425
It's so unfair.

00:10:30.345 --> 00:10:32.585
I lived a good life.

00:10:34.025 --> 00:10:37.065
I didn't drink, I didn't smoke.

00:10:37.585 --> 00:10:40.225
I gave everything to my work.

00:10:42.065 --> 00:10:43.505
And what did I get?

00:10:44.865 --> 00:10:48.865
A tumor… and a pink slip.

00:10:51.425 --> 00:10:53.025
How is that fair?

00:10:58.265 --> 00:11:00.145
It’s so damn unfair.

00:11:01.745 --> 00:11:03.225
It’s okay, Nava.

00:11:03.745 --> 00:11:06.185
It’s okay. I’m right here.

00:11:06.945 --> 00:11:08.745
I’m by your side.

00:11:08.825 --> 00:11:11.865
I’ll stay here until you're healed.

00:11:14.185 --> 00:11:15.505
I promise.

00:11:17.185 --> 00:11:18.065
You will be okay.

00:11:22.185 --> 00:11:23.425
You will be okay, Nava.

00:11:25.905 --> 00:11:27.425
Koh Larn, this way please!

00:11:28.065 --> 00:11:29.265
Thank you.

00:11:29.345 --> 00:11:30.825
FERRY - CHAI WATTHANA 2

00:11:30.905 --> 00:11:32.025
Thank you.

00:11:33.145 --> 00:11:34.465
Thank you.

00:11:35.385 --> 00:11:37.025
Koh Larn, this way!

00:11:38.305 --> 00:11:39.505
Thank you, enjoy your trip.

00:11:40.105 --> 00:11:42.105
Koh Larn, this way! Thank you.

00:11:42.185 --> 00:11:43.465
Enjoy your trip.

00:11:44.065 --> 00:11:46.105
Hey, young man!
You filling in for DinDin today?

00:11:46.705 --> 00:11:48.025
Yes. I'm taking over for DinDin today.

00:11:48.625 --> 00:11:50.065
Did he trick you into doing this?

00:11:51.185 --> 00:11:53.265
Not at all. I'm doing this willingly.

00:11:53.345 --> 00:11:54.745
Alright then.

00:11:55.265 --> 00:11:56.505
Alright!

00:11:57.345 --> 00:12:00.265
Koh Larn, this way! Koh Larn, over here!

00:12:13.185 --> 00:12:14.705
Mr. Sailom,

00:12:15.945 --> 00:12:19.665
I want to thank you for
coming back to see me.

00:12:21.905 --> 00:12:22.945
You're welcome.

00:12:25.225 --> 00:12:27.945
During our sessions,

00:12:28.025 --> 00:12:32.305
if there's anything you'd like to share,

00:12:32.385 --> 00:12:36.825
please tell me anything.
I'm here to listen.

00:12:39.945 --> 00:12:40.785
Yes.

00:12:42.385 --> 00:12:46.345
And everything we discuss today

00:12:46.425 --> 00:12:50.065
will be kept confidential
for your treatment only.

00:12:50.945 --> 00:12:52.985
Do I have your permission?

00:12:58.865 --> 00:12:59.705
Yes, you do.

00:13:01.745 --> 00:13:05.145
Thank you very much. So…

00:13:05.225 --> 00:13:07.625
did you have anything
for breakfast this morning?

00:13:10.785 --> 00:13:12.265
Not yet.

00:13:13.065 --> 00:13:14.985
I didn't really have an appetite.

00:13:16.945 --> 00:13:21.825
You didn't have breakfast
because you didn't feel like eating.

00:13:21.905 --> 00:13:26.225
Is there any food you particularly like?

00:13:28.105 --> 00:13:30.705
Well… fish steak.

00:13:30.785 --> 00:13:33.305
Oh, fish steak.

00:13:33.385 --> 00:13:38.905
What kind of fish? Dory or Salmon?

00:13:40.945 --> 00:13:42.145
Salmon.

00:13:42.225 --> 00:13:44.985
Oh! I love salmon too!

00:13:45.505 --> 00:13:51.105
And do you usually
have it with any side dishes?

00:13:51.185 --> 00:13:54.705
Like som tam, fries, or salad?

00:13:55.865 --> 00:14:02.305
Mashed potatoes, fries, and soup.

00:14:18.145 --> 00:14:19.225
Sailom.

00:14:22.945 --> 00:14:25.465
Where would you like to go today?

00:14:27.145 --> 00:14:30.105
I’d rather go home.

00:14:31.425 --> 00:14:33.985
Let’s go to your place. To my car.

00:14:49.345 --> 00:14:50.785
Can I try?

00:14:50.865 --> 00:14:52.865
-Can you?
-Of course!

00:14:55.305 --> 00:14:56.545
Go ahead!

00:14:57.865 --> 00:15:01.065
-Are you sure this is for Somtam?
-Right?

00:15:01.145 --> 00:15:03.345
-What about this?
-Looks good!

00:15:03.425 --> 00:15:05.905
-Tam Luang Phrabang, please.
-Sure!

00:15:05.985 --> 00:15:09.185
-Great job!
-Yes! Green or red?

00:15:28.825 --> 00:15:31.705
They might not look
as fancy as restaurant dishes,

00:15:31.785 --> 00:15:33.345
but I guarantee they're delicious.

00:15:35.745 --> 00:15:39.025
I think they look and taste amazing

00:15:40.065 --> 00:15:42.905
because you made me
do so much of the work.

00:15:43.625 --> 00:15:44.665
But I seasoned it.

00:15:46.105 --> 00:15:48.585
I watched a Japanese food show once.

00:15:48.665 --> 00:15:53.985
They said the secret to
delicious food is all in the cutting.

00:15:54.065 --> 00:15:56.265
Okay, I give up.

00:15:56.345 --> 00:15:57.545
Do you know why?

00:15:57.625 --> 00:16:00.585
-Why?
-Because I’m starving. Let's eat.

00:16:02.265 --> 00:16:03.945
Here, try your own masterpiece first.

00:16:04.025 --> 00:16:05.225
Here.

00:16:11.025 --> 00:16:13.305
Nom.

00:16:15.225 --> 00:16:16.065
Good?

00:16:16.585 --> 00:16:18.705
-Mmm!
-What does "Mmm" mean?

00:16:19.345 --> 00:16:20.865
-Good.
-Really?

00:16:21.385 --> 00:16:22.785
It’s a bit too spicy for you.

00:16:25.185 --> 00:16:26.545
My turn. Let me try some.

00:16:28.625 --> 00:16:30.305
One, two…

00:16:30.385 --> 00:16:32.745
-Wow! This is so good!
-Not yet!

00:17:00.105 --> 00:17:01.665
I hope your grandma can eat this.

00:17:06.625 --> 00:17:07.905
Old man.

00:17:08.985 --> 00:17:10.385
Take your damn money back.

00:17:12.105 --> 00:17:14.625
I never asked you to pay for
my grandma's medical bill.

00:17:16.224 --> 00:17:18.464
I already paid. Just keep it.

00:17:18.545 --> 00:17:21.585
Do you think I can’t afford the bill?

00:17:25.865 --> 00:17:27.625
That's not what I think.

00:17:28.865 --> 00:17:30.865
I just don't want to see you struggling.

00:17:31.945 --> 00:17:33.665
Struggling? What struggle?

00:17:33.745 --> 00:17:34.905
I'm fine!

00:17:34.985 --> 00:17:37.585
Just admit that you have money problems.

00:17:38.265 --> 00:17:42.585
Why else would you be singing,
taking boat tickets, and making sweets?

00:17:42.665 --> 00:17:44.385
That’s my business!

00:17:44.905 --> 00:17:46.065
Stay out of it!

00:17:46.145 --> 00:17:48.025
Because you’re my employee!

00:17:49.105 --> 00:17:50.905
If you don't show up,

00:17:50.985 --> 00:17:52.705
my shop has nothing to sell!

00:17:54.745 --> 00:17:58.145
If you really want to pay me back,

00:17:58.905 --> 00:18:00.585
I can deduct it from your salary.

00:18:03.825 --> 00:18:04.945
Dick.

00:18:06.945 --> 00:18:08.545
But you have to pay interest.

00:18:12.945 --> 00:18:13.825
What interest?

00:18:14.705 --> 00:18:16.305
Drink with me every night.

00:18:20.545 --> 00:18:21.785
Just say you’re horny.

00:18:23.265 --> 00:18:25.585
Yeah, I’m horny.

00:19:08.705 --> 00:19:11.625
Is camping with a boyfriend
on your bucket list too?

00:19:12.705 --> 00:19:13.705
Yeah.

00:19:14.505 --> 00:19:18.225
This trip is actually one of them.

00:19:22.185 --> 00:19:25.985
I’ve wanted to go camping
with a boyfriend for so long,

00:19:26.705 --> 00:19:29.505
but I never had a partner

00:19:30.225 --> 00:19:31.545
and time.

00:19:32.585 --> 00:19:34.425
About when you got fired…

00:19:36.625 --> 00:19:39.385
After I found out I had cancer…

00:19:40.745 --> 00:19:43.385
I didn't want to live anymore.

00:19:45.025 --> 00:19:46.385
I just thought

00:19:47.225 --> 00:19:49.825
I'd try everything I'd never done.

00:19:50.985 --> 00:19:55.825
Like… drinking,

00:19:57.945 --> 00:19:59.225
hitting up host bars,

00:20:00.825 --> 00:20:02.505
and having a boyfriend.

00:20:04.305 --> 00:20:05.785
I wanted to live it up,

00:20:05.865 --> 00:20:08.025
to make this life feel worth it.

00:20:09.865 --> 00:20:12.265
Is there anything else you want to do?

00:20:17.705 --> 00:20:18.665
Well…

00:20:19.385 --> 00:20:20.585
I do.

00:20:21.425 --> 00:20:22.945
There are places I want to go.

00:20:24.225 --> 00:20:27.185
I spent all my time working
and never went anywhere.

00:20:31.025 --> 00:20:33.305
Where… do you want to go?

00:20:37.865 --> 00:20:39.185
I…

00:20:39.825 --> 00:20:41.585
want to travel abroad.

00:20:43.545 --> 00:20:46.265
I've never even been to Japan.

00:20:48.225 --> 00:20:49.265
Go…

00:20:49.785 --> 00:20:51.425
see the London Eye,

00:20:52.825 --> 00:20:54.545
try…

00:20:54.625 --> 00:20:57.865
parachuting or skydiving,

00:20:59.025 --> 00:21:02.105
visit the Great Wall,

00:21:03.225 --> 00:21:07.505
Bali, Hawaii… so many places.

00:21:07.585 --> 00:21:08.505
Mm-hmm.

00:21:21.185 --> 00:21:22.665
If that's what you want,

00:21:24.465 --> 00:21:27.705
you need to get better first, okay?

00:21:29.105 --> 00:21:31.185
Once you're better,

00:21:32.425 --> 00:21:36.105
I'll take you everywhere you want to go.

00:21:36.985 --> 00:21:38.145
I promise.

00:22:01.625 --> 00:22:03.705
So… where should we go first?

00:22:04.305 --> 00:22:05.985
I think…

00:22:07.465 --> 00:22:09.065
London sounds interesting.

00:22:09.585 --> 00:22:11.585
I've always wanted
to see the London Eye too.

00:22:11.665 --> 00:22:12.665
Really?

00:22:18.545 --> 00:22:20.185
Why are you crying?

00:23:05.385 --> 00:23:06.905
Nabnueng,

00:23:07.785 --> 00:23:09.225
you already know this.

00:23:09.905 --> 00:23:15.705
The best form of healing is
rebuilding trust in humanity.

00:23:16.225 --> 00:23:21.345
Or making Sailom trust someone

00:23:21.425 --> 00:23:23.345
and learning to lean on those around him.

00:23:38.625 --> 00:23:39.825
Sailom!

00:23:46.705 --> 00:23:48.585
-Are you ready?
-Ready!

00:23:49.225 --> 00:23:50.465
Let's go then.

00:24:20.025 --> 00:24:22.945
Do you usually enjoy watching movies?

00:24:24.105 --> 00:24:25.225
I love them.

00:24:25.305 --> 00:24:26.665
How often do you watch them?

00:24:26.745 --> 00:24:28.505
About once a week.

00:24:28.585 --> 00:24:30.585
Wow! Once a week?

00:24:30.665 --> 00:24:33.585
-Yes.
-That means you watch four movies a month.

00:24:34.665 --> 00:24:35.585
That's right.

00:24:36.265 --> 00:24:39.385
Is there a particular movie that you love?

00:24:40.625 --> 00:24:44.145
I really like "First Love."

00:24:45.265 --> 00:24:49.945
Oh, so you're a fan of romantic movies?

00:24:50.705 --> 00:24:52.545
I love that one too!

00:24:52.625 --> 00:24:54.145
-Really?
-"First Love"

00:25:06.825 --> 00:25:09.265
I’m going to let it go now.
Slow and steady.

00:25:09.345 --> 00:25:11.545
-Like this?
-A bit more. Watch out for the string.

00:25:12.785 --> 00:25:14.665
Do you feel that? Feel the wind?

00:25:14.745 --> 00:25:15.785
Run.

00:25:17.585 --> 00:25:19.945
Like this, then back to this way.

00:25:21.905 --> 00:25:22.865
Give it a try!

00:26:22.945 --> 00:26:25.025
How are you feeling today, Mr. Sailom?

00:26:26.625 --> 00:26:28.345
I feel like…

00:26:28.425 --> 00:26:30.705
I can touch other people again.

00:26:31.985 --> 00:26:33.145
Really?

00:26:33.745 --> 00:26:38.105
I heard you did some activities
with your friends at the beach?

00:26:38.185 --> 00:26:39.025
Yes.

00:26:40.345 --> 00:26:41.985
We played Monkey in the Middle

00:26:42.065 --> 00:26:44.545
and flew kites together.

00:26:44.625 --> 00:26:48.185
So, during Monkey in the Middle,

00:26:48.265 --> 00:26:51.505
you could touch your friends?

00:27:00.505 --> 00:27:01.665
Yes.

00:27:03.025 --> 00:27:05.585
While we were chasing the ball,

00:27:05.665 --> 00:27:09.425
I was touching and bumping into others.

00:27:10.225 --> 00:27:12.065
-Yes.
-In that case,

00:27:12.145 --> 00:27:16.225
could you try touching my hand
like you did with your friends?

00:27:24.025 --> 00:27:26.305
Like when you touched your friends.

00:27:27.825 --> 00:27:28.745
Okay.

00:27:46.025 --> 00:27:47.305
You’ve improved so much.

00:27:47.385 --> 00:27:50.945
Now, may I have your permission
to touch your arm?

00:27:54.065 --> 00:27:54.985
Yes, you may.

00:28:12.745 --> 00:28:14.585
Well done!

00:28:14.665 --> 00:28:16.225
This is wonderful!

00:28:17.185 --> 00:28:18.305
I actually did it!

00:28:19.145 --> 00:28:20.425
You were amazing!

00:28:48.905 --> 00:28:49.985
DinDin.

00:28:51.705 --> 00:28:53.105
Come have a drink with me.

00:28:57.265 --> 00:28:59.505
Your life must be so stressful.

00:29:00.145 --> 00:29:01.665
I see you drink all day.

00:29:03.145 --> 00:29:03.985
Mind your own business.

00:29:07.065 --> 00:29:08.345
DinDin,

00:29:08.865 --> 00:29:09.985
are you gonna join me?

00:29:10.705 --> 00:29:13.585
Yeah, let me finish
checking the stock first.

00:29:36.545 --> 00:29:39.665
What are you doing here?

00:29:41.425 --> 00:29:43.545
Just checking if you're done yet.

00:29:50.225 --> 00:29:51.265
Be real with me.

00:29:52.785 --> 00:29:54.025
You’re horny?

00:29:58.345 --> 00:29:59.865
Just let me finish this first.

00:30:30.865 --> 00:30:31.905
Hey!

00:30:37.345 --> 00:30:39.265
If you don't stop messing with me,

00:30:40.465 --> 00:30:42.465
you’re gonna be eating my fist.

00:30:43.705 --> 00:30:45.385
Going to punch me again?

00:30:46.545 --> 00:30:49.705
Is it a tradition to throw
a punch before we kiss?

00:30:52.305 --> 00:30:55.945
Can we try kissing without
the punching for once?

00:30:59.145 --> 00:31:00.665
Don't want to have a sore lip.

00:32:06.545 --> 00:32:09.025
Come on, put your clothes on.

00:32:09.945 --> 00:32:11.265
Why?

00:32:12.865 --> 00:32:13.905
Well…

00:32:14.825 --> 00:32:17.345
we go our separate ways after we're done.

00:32:23.585 --> 00:32:27.065
Can I stay like this for a little longer?

00:33:38.145 --> 00:33:41.345
SAVINGS ACCOUNT: 47,596.59 BAHT

00:33:41.945 --> 00:33:44.745
I… want to travel abroad.

00:33:49.585 --> 00:33:50.785
If that's what you want,

00:33:52.905 --> 00:33:55.865
you need to get better first, okay?

00:33:57.505 --> 00:33:59.905
Once you're better,

00:34:00.865 --> 00:34:04.625
I'll take you everywhere you want to go.

00:34:31.744 --> 00:34:34.425
Nava. I got a lot of vegetables today.

00:34:34.505 --> 00:34:36.385
I was thinking of making stir-fry…

00:34:39.025 --> 00:34:41.425
Nava? Where are you going?

00:34:42.185 --> 00:34:43.264
I want to go home.

00:34:44.425 --> 00:34:45.744
Why?

00:34:46.385 --> 00:34:47.945
Why so suddenly?

00:34:48.025 --> 00:34:49.665
Is there something wrong at home?

00:34:51.344 --> 00:34:52.945
Everything's fine at home.

00:34:53.905 --> 00:34:55.625
I just want to go home to die.

00:34:55.705 --> 00:34:57.025
Die?

00:34:57.905 --> 00:34:59.705
I thought we talked about this.

00:35:00.225 --> 00:35:02.425
You were going to get treatment.

00:35:03.625 --> 00:35:05.105
I don't think I ever said that.

00:35:06.385 --> 00:35:07.585
You just assumed it yourself.

00:35:09.705 --> 00:35:10.825
Nava…

00:35:12.825 --> 00:35:14.545
I'm asking you seriously.

00:35:16.745 --> 00:35:18.225
Did you ever…

00:35:19.625 --> 00:35:21.065
love me at all?

00:35:23.225 --> 00:35:25.905
Or am I just some host

00:35:25.985 --> 00:35:28.145
you used for fun before you died?

00:35:31.305 --> 00:35:33.985
I feel like I mean nothing to you.

00:35:34.505 --> 00:35:39.705
You want to give up, you want to die.

00:35:39.785 --> 00:35:41.065
You keep saying that!

00:35:42.985 --> 00:35:44.625
Have you ever thought…

00:35:45.985 --> 00:35:47.425
about how I live…

00:35:48.545 --> 00:35:50.145
if you’re gone?

00:35:52.665 --> 00:35:53.945
Sky…

00:35:55.145 --> 00:35:57.545
If you wanted to die from the start,

00:36:01.305 --> 00:36:03.425
why did you make me love you?

00:36:10.105 --> 00:36:11.425
Sky…

00:36:12.225 --> 00:36:13.425
I’m sorry.

00:36:16.625 --> 00:36:17.785
I’m so sorry.

00:36:23.825 --> 00:36:25.265
I do love you, Sky.

00:36:28.105 --> 00:36:29.105
But…

00:36:29.865 --> 00:36:31.465
I’ve run out of money.

00:36:34.105 --> 00:36:36.145
I can't afford the treatment anymore.

00:36:37.985 --> 00:36:39.625
I just can't.

00:36:43.465 --> 00:36:45.025
I don’t have the money.

00:37:00.585 --> 00:37:01.505
Nava!

00:37:02.105 --> 00:37:04.945
Nava, have a seat!

00:37:16.825 --> 00:37:18.625
Are you nervous?

00:37:19.665 --> 00:37:21.985
A little. But I'm more hungry.

00:37:23.425 --> 00:37:26.945
Hang in there. You can eat
whatever you want after the surgery.

00:37:27.785 --> 00:37:32.865
I’ll take you everywhere,

00:37:32.945 --> 00:37:35.185
and we'll do everything

00:37:36.065 --> 00:37:37.505
on your list.

00:37:38.185 --> 00:37:39.025
Fight on.

00:37:45.825 --> 00:37:47.985
Is this a hospital or a maze?

00:37:48.065 --> 00:37:49.265
Took me forever to find this room.

00:37:50.305 --> 00:37:51.465
I brought you some oranges.

00:37:51.985 --> 00:37:52.865
Man, it’s you…

00:37:53.865 --> 00:37:57.665
Hey, show some respect
to your "Major Sponsor," will you?

00:37:58.785 --> 00:38:00.305
What sponsor?

00:38:01.865 --> 00:38:03.705
Haven’t you told him yet?

00:38:10.265 --> 00:38:11.185
Cheers!

00:38:24.785 --> 00:38:25.705
Sky?

00:38:26.225 --> 00:38:27.585
Pi Man,

00:38:28.625 --> 00:38:29.905
please help my boyfriend.

00:38:34.465 --> 00:38:38.025
Sky never asked me for anything,

00:38:38.105 --> 00:38:39.865
unlike the other hosts.

00:38:40.745 --> 00:38:43.545
That’s why I like him.

00:38:44.825 --> 00:38:49.505
Thanks for telling me
you like my boyfriend in front of me.

00:38:52.305 --> 00:38:55.345
What does that have to do
with the money for my treatment?

00:38:56.545 --> 00:38:59.425
Has the cancer reached your brain?

00:39:00.105 --> 00:39:01.505
It’s in my colon.

00:39:01.585 --> 00:39:03.305
Whatever.

00:39:03.385 --> 00:39:04.865
But use your head.

00:39:04.945 --> 00:39:06.985
Someone who
never asks for anything for himself,

00:39:08.345 --> 00:39:10.945
but comes begging me
to save his boyfriend…

00:39:11.465 --> 00:39:12.945
Think about how much he loves you.

00:39:13.825 --> 00:39:15.665
It hurts just talking about it.

00:39:23.905 --> 00:39:26.185
Thank you so much, Pi Man.

00:39:26.785 --> 00:39:28.985
Huh? What did you call me?

00:39:29.825 --> 00:39:31.025
Pi Man.

00:39:35.625 --> 00:39:37.385
And I'm sorry

00:39:38.905 --> 00:39:40.625
for everything in the past.

00:39:42.265 --> 00:39:43.665
Just get well soon

00:39:43.745 --> 00:39:45.905
so you can work and pay me back.

00:39:45.985 --> 00:39:50.385
Do you know how many drinks
this money could have bought?

00:39:52.105 --> 00:39:53.185
Thank you.

00:39:53.825 --> 00:39:54.745
I’m going.

00:39:55.745 --> 00:39:57.345
Oh, and don't worry.

00:39:57.425 --> 00:39:59.905
I won't use this money
as an excuse to mess with Sky.

00:40:00.665 --> 00:40:01.705
There are plenty of other hosts.

00:40:04.265 --> 00:40:05.185
Pi Man,

00:40:06.105 --> 00:40:07.825
I thank you again.

00:40:09.945 --> 00:40:11.505
Happy to help.

00:40:12.785 --> 00:40:14.585
Pi Man, your hand…

00:40:14.665 --> 00:40:16.105
Just a little bit.

00:40:27.105 --> 00:40:28.705
Thank you, Sky.

00:40:29.585 --> 00:40:30.705
For doing all of this for me.

00:40:32.065 --> 00:40:33.425
Don't thank me.

00:40:33.945 --> 00:40:35.185
You don’t have to.

00:40:36.145 --> 00:40:39.505
Just get better and stay with me…

00:40:40.385 --> 00:40:41.465
That’s all I need.

00:42:13.025 --> 00:42:14.385
Sailom…

00:42:20.185 --> 00:42:22.025
Will you be my boyfriend?

00:42:33.585 --> 00:42:35.465
Is it going to be a burden

00:42:38.705 --> 00:42:40.945
to be with a broken man like me?

00:42:48.425 --> 00:42:49.545
I don't know.

00:42:51.385 --> 00:42:52.905
We’ll have to find out.

00:43:04.425 --> 00:43:05.745
In that case…

00:43:09.265 --> 00:43:10.865
do we try kissing?

00:44:51.305 --> 00:44:52.425
Are you really cured?

00:44:52.505 --> 00:44:56.945
Cured or not, the doctor
asked me to be his boyfriend!

00:45:00.185 --> 00:45:01.465
The boss sent me to collect the interest.

00:45:02.505 --> 00:45:05.505
I'll do whatever
it takes to keep this house.

00:45:06.425 --> 00:45:09.825
My mother asked me to help
my sick biological sister.

00:45:09.905 --> 00:45:12.105
-How?
-A bone marrow transplant.

00:45:12.185 --> 00:45:14.785
It has to come from a full
sibling with the same parents.

00:45:15.385 --> 00:45:16.185
Have you seen your sister?

00:45:16.265 --> 00:45:18.065
I just saw her taking out the trash.

00:45:18.665 --> 00:45:19.745
Who the hell are these bastards?